Brazil Sept. IGP-M Index Rises 0.52% in Second Preview

-- B y   F e r n a n d o   S i m o n
-- 
2011-09-19T11:02:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/brazil-sept-igp-m-index-rises-0-52-in-second-preview-table-.html
The following table is a summary of the second
preview of the IGP-M inflation report from the Getulio Vargas Foundation
in Rio de Janeiro.  The IGP-M second preview covers the first 20 days
of data collection.  NOTE: IGP-M inflation is composed of wholesale Prices (60% weight), 
consumer prices (30% weight) and construction costs (10% weight).
IGP-M has a final figure and two previews.  The final figure covers
from the 21st of previous month to the 20th of current month.  SOURCE: Getulio Vargas Foundation (FGV)  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fernando Simon in  Sao Paulo  at   fsimon5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
